data.description: This home is nestled on a quiet cul-de-sac in the heart of Virginia Beach, featuring three bedrooms and two baths.  Offering comfort and convenience, the open and spacious layout features a welcoming living room, and a cozy kitchen with dining area. The primary bedroom boasts a private en-suite bathroom, while two additional bedrooms provide versatility for guests or a home office. The converted garage provides yet, another flex space for your home gym or play room. Outside, provides a large private space for planting a garden,  gathering with friends and those summer cook-outs.
